# Sprint 05: Copy Styles from taskboard-supabase (UI & Glass Effects)
# S05.ptl

**Goal:** Copy and implement UI styles and glass-effect system from `taskboard-supabase` into `totem-view`, with focus on glassmorphism tokens, utility classes, modal/overlay pattern, and reusable glass components.

**Source of truth:**
- `taskboard-supabase/client/src/style.css` — variables, @layer components/utilities
- `taskboard-supabase/totem/docs/UI_GLASS_EFFECT_SUMMARY.md` — glass recipe, levels, accent, modal/button patterns
- taskboard-supabase components: `Button.vue` (glass variants), `Card.vue`, `.modal-glass` usage in modals/panels

**Invariants:**
- S04-INVARIANTS.md (if present); after S05: create S05-INVARIANTS.md (glass tokens, class names, Safari backdrop-filter rule).

**Gate:** OPEN

## Track 1: Style foundation
- task: S05-T1-GlassTokensAndVariables.pd
- task: S05-T2-GlassUtilitiesAndComponents.pd

## Track 2: Glass UI implementation
- task: S05-T3-ModalOverlayPattern.pd
- task: S05-T4-GlassButtonsAndCards.pd

---

**Result (sprint outcome):** Текущий UI totem-view **не соответствует** дизайну taskboard-supabase. Токены, классы и паттерны портированы, но визуальная и композиционная parity с референсом не достигнута; требуется отдельная задача на выравнивание дизайна.
